languages.text: Вольному Торговцу не удалось обнаружить следов присутствия имперской цивилизации на замерзшей планете несмотря на документы, подтверждающие сей факт. Возможно, дело в недостаточно мощных авгурах корабля.

traits.locale_text: Вольному Торговцу не удалось обнаружить следов присутствия имперской цивилизации на замерзшей планете несмотря на документы, подтверждающие сей факт. Возможно, дело в недостаточно мощных авгурах корабля.

languages.text: The Rogue Trader failed to uncover traces of human civilisation on the frozen planet, despite possessing documents attesting to that fact. Perhaps the problem lies in the ship's augurs — they are simply not powerful enough.

traits.locale_text: The Rogue Trader failed to uncover traces of an Imperial civilisation on the frozen planet, despite possessing documents attesting to that fact. Perhaps the problem lies in the ship's augurs — they are simply not powerful enough. Or the documents are simply lying.

languages.text: 尽管行商浪人已经得到了足以证明真相的资料，但虚空舰并没有在这颗冰冻的行星上发现任何人类文明的痕迹。或许问题出在舰船的俄歇矩阵上，目前的矩阵功率还不够强大。
languages.original_text: The Rogue Trader failed to uncover traces of human civilisation on the frozen planet, despite possessing documents attesting to that fact. Perhaps the problem lies in the ship's augurs — they are simply not powerful enough.

traits.locale_text: 尽管行商浪人已经得到了足以证明真相的资料，但虚空舰并没有在这颗冰冻的行星上发现任何帝国文明的痕迹。或许问题出在舰船的俄歇矩阵不够强大，又或许因为那些资料上的记录都是谎言。

languages.text: 自由開拓者は、その事実を証明する文書を所有していたにもかかわらず、冷凍惑星では人類の文明の痕跡を発見できなかった。おそらく問題は船のスキャナーにある。単にスキャナーの力が足りないのだ。
languages.original_text: The Rogue Trader failed to uncover traces of human civilisation on the frozen planet, despite possessing documents attesting to that fact. Perhaps the problem lies in the ship's augurs — they are simply not powerful enough.

traits.locale_text: 自由開拓者は、その事実を証明する文書を所有していたにもかかわらず、冷凍惑星では人類の文明の痕跡を発見できなかった。おそらく問題は船のスキャナーにある。単にスキャナーの力が足りないのだ。

languages.text: {mf|El|La} Comerciante Independiente no ha encontrado rastros de civilización Imperial en el planeta helado a pesar de los documentos que la atestiguan. Tal vez el problema esté en los augures de la nave, que no son lo bastante potentes.
languages.original_text: The Rogue Trader failed to uncover traces of human civilisation on the frozen planet, despite possessing documents attesting to that fact. Perhaps the problem lies in the ship's augurs — they are simply not powerful enough.

traits.locale_text: {mf|El|La} Comerciante Independiente no ha encontrado rastros de civilización Imperial en el planeta helado a pesar de los documentos que la atestiguan. Tal vez el problema esté en los augures de la nave, a los que les falta potencia. O tal vez los documentos sean falsos.

languages.text: {mf|Der Freihändler|Die Freihändlerin} konnte auf dem gefrorenen Planeten trotz entsprechender Dokumente keine Spuren einer menschlichen Zivilisation entdecken. Vielleicht sind die Auguren des Schiffs das Problem. Sie sind einfach nicht effizient genug.
languages.original_text: The Rogue Trader failed to uncover traces of human civilisation on the frozen planet, despite possessing documents attesting to that fact. Perhaps the problem lies in the ship's augurs — they are simply not powerful enough.

traits.locale_text: {mf|Der Freihändler|Die Freihändlerin} konnte auf dem gefrorenen Planeten trotz entsprechender Dokumente keine Spuren einer imperialen Zivilisation entdecken. Vielleicht sind die Auguren des Schiffs das Problem. Sie sind einfach nicht effizient genug. Oder die Dokumente lügen.

languages.text: {mf|Le libre-marchand|La libre-marchande} n'a pas réussi à retrouver les traces d'une civilisation humaine sur la planète gelée, malgré les documents attestant de son existence. Le problème vient peut-être des augures du vaisseau qui ne sont pas assez puissants.
languages.original_text: The Rogue Trader failed to uncover traces of human civilisation on the frozen planet, despite possessing documents attesting to that fact. Perhaps the problem lies in the ship's augurs — they are simply not powerful enough.

traits.locale_text: {mf|Le libre-marchand|La libre-marchande} n'a pas réussi à retrouver les traces d'une civilisation impériale sur la planète gelée, malgré les documents attestant de son existence. Le problème vient peut-être des augures du vaisseau qui ne sont pas assez puissants. Ou bien les documents sont tout simplement faux.

languages.text: Hür Tacir, dokümanlar bu gerçeği doğrulamasına rağmen donuk gezegende insan uygarlığına dair izler bulmayı başaramadı. Belki de sorun geminin alametlerindedir, belki de yeterince güçlü değillerdir.
languages.original_text: The Rogue Trader failed to uncover traces of human civilisation on the frozen planet, despite possessing documents attesting to that fact. Perhaps the problem lies in the ship's augurs — they are simply not powerful enough.

traits.locale_text: Hür Tacir, dokümanlar bu gerçeği doğruluyor olsa da, donmuş gezegendeki insan uygarlığına dair izler bulmayı başaramadı. Belki de sorun geminin alametlerindedir, belki de yeterince güçlü değillerdir.
